        "name": "Set LED State Payload",
        "func": "// Slider gui gia tri 0-100 -> format + dong bo switch ve dung trang thai\nvar b = Number(msg.payload);\nreturn [\n    { payload: { brightness: b } },   // [0] -> MQTT (lenh cho ESP)\n    { payload: b > 0 }                // [1] -> switch (dong bo UI)\n];",
